OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,FA former Royal Mail employee has told
OL,7,FITV Meridian that staff would hide
OL,8,Fmail during audits and drive it in
OL,9,Florries around the M25 until
OL,10,Finspectors were gone.
OL,12,FWe spoke with two Royal Mail ex-staff
OL,13,Fwho worked in Tonbridge for a number
OL,14,Fof years.
OL,16,FIn shocking claims, they allege that
OL,17,Fletters would be hidden before
OL,18,Finspectors even arrived. One
OL,19,Fwhistleblower agreed to speak with us
OL,20,Fon camera anonymously.
