OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,F"They knew they was coming so they'd
OL,7,Fhide the mail," he said.
OL,9,F"Whether that was send it out in vans,
OL,10,Fknowing full well it's coming back.
OL,11,FHide it somewhere in the depot or in
OL,12,Fother depots, or put it in lorries and
OL,13,Fdrive it round the M25 until they were
OL,14,Fgone."
OL,16,F"There's just more and more and more
OL,17,Fmail, always letters, just sat in
OL,18,Fframes. Unless they are their
OL,19,Fprioritised parcel with a tracked,
OL,20,Fthey just get left behind...collect
OL,21,Fdust.
