OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,F"They don't want letters because they
OL,7,Fdon't make money. Whereas parcels make
OL,8,Fmoney."
OL,10,FRoyal Mail wouldn't speak on camera,
OL,11,Fbut refute the allegations put forward
OL,12,Fby ex-employees.
OL,14,FThe company says it's not an accurate
OL,15,Freflection of how quality of service
OL,16,Fis measured. Saying that quality of
OL,17,Fservice statistics are recorded
OL,18,Fdigitally every day (rather than
OL,19,Fassessed through visual checks) and
OL,20,Fare audited by senior management at
OL,21,Fleast weekly.
