OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,FThey added that they have an
OL,7,Findependent quality measurer, overseen
OL,8,Fby regulator Ofcom, which has recently
OL,9,Fshown a significant improvement in
OL,10,Fservice levels in Tonbridge.
OL,12,FThe allegations come as some residents
OL,13,Fin Paddock Wood, Kent - along with
OL,14,Fparts of Tonbridge and Tunbridge Wells
OL,15,F- are facing severe postal delays in
OL,16,Ftheir area.
OL,18,FAn ITV Meridian investigation found
OL,19,Fthat some letters have been taking
OL,20,Fmore than two weeks to arrive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
