OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,FResidents say that late letters have
OL,7,Fcaused them to miss important medical
OL,8,Fappointments and blood test results,
OL,9,Fwith one woman telling us the delays
OL,10,Fhave made her chronic back condition
OL,11,Fworse, as she isn't always receiving
OL,12,Fthe medication that keeps it under
OL,13,Fcontrol.
OL,15,FLaura Manuel said: "There's been quite
OL,16,Fa few times the hospital's called me,
OL,17,F'You're meant to be at this
OL,18,Fappointment', and I know nothing about
OL,19,Fit.
