OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,F"I've missed medication that is
OL,7,Fdelivered by Royal Mail.
OL,9,F"Physically it causes a lot of pain,
OL,10,Fbut more so it's frustrating because
OL,11,Fthen I'm having to ask for help. I'm a
OL,12,F42 year old woman that shouldn't need
OL,13,Fto ask for help."
OL,15,FAnother Paddock Wood resident, Tom
OL,16,FAbbey, decided to take matters into
OL,17,Fhis own hands by sending a joint
OL,18,Fcomplaint to Royal Mail from residents.
