OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,FHe says that after going on a Facebook
OL,7,Fcommunity page, he found "this whole
OL,8,Fmassive problem."
OL,10,FRoyal Mail told us that Tonbridge is a
OL,11,Fdifficult area to recruit in, adding
OL,12,Fthat more newbuild developments have
OL,13,Fincreased demand. And that Paddock
OL,14,FWood is a highly skilled delivery
OL,15,Froute, where many houses have names
OL,16,Fand not numbers.
OL,18,FTunbridge Wells MP, Mike Martin said
OL,19,Fhe's had a "long backwards and
OL,20,Fforwards" with Royal Mail about the
OL,21,Fpostal delivery delays in the area.
