OL,3,CFormer Royal Mail employee says staff
OL,4,Chid mail during audits
OL,6,F"I met with them recently and they
OL,7,Fadmitted that they'd had leadership
OL,8,Fand recruitment problems in the TN
OL,9,Fpostcode, so across Tunbridge Wells.
OL,11,FTunbridge Wells MP, Mike Martin,
OL,12,Fthinks people will see improvements to
OL,13,Fpostal delays in his area
OL,15,F"I think this is actually a long
OL,16,Frunning problem. I do think we are
OL,17,Fgoing to see improvements, hopefully,
OL,18,Fthey've promised me they are going to
OL,19,Fmake those improvements. But I think
OL,20,Fit's going to be a slow burn."
